  "summary": {
    "zh": "一辆 F1 赛车是风洞、CFD、七通道台架与驾驶模拟器协同打磨的产物，叠加可转让件、列名件与开源件的规则边界，由分属不同专业小组的数百人共同推进。",
    "en": "An F1 car is honed by wind tunnel, CFD, seven-post rig and driving simulator in concert, layered onto Transferable, Listed and Open-source component rules, by hundreds across specialist groups."
  },
